      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，流程是：main上init → 切出feature → feature上feat → 切回main → 合并feature。这样合并箭头会正确指向main，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge feature"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个顺序。合并后main应该包含两条线的历史，能清晰看到feature被整合进来了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "feature"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了。我检查一下：init在main起点，feature分支从那里分出，feat提交在feature线上，然后切回main做了merge，feature的历史现在并到main上了。",
      "elements_involved": [
